  <brief_summary>
    <textblock>
      This is a randomized pilot trial to evaluate the impact of a customizable stroke education&#xD;
      app (vs standard of care discharge education) on patient satisfaction and education&#xD;
      retention. The impact of the intervention will be assessed 7, 30, and 90 days post-discharge.&#xD;
    </textblock>
  </brief_summary>
